From: "Dhia Eddine (via Claude)" <dhia-work@local>
Date: Sat, 18 Jul 2026 23:38:35 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Add ExerciseSet model + Gemini-based vocabulary generation

- New Anex enum (VOCABULARY, GRAMMAR, LISTENING_WRITING, SPEAKING)
- New ExerciseSet model tied to Lesson, holds generated items as JSON
- Expanded GameType with vocabulary/grammar/listening/speaking game types
- Game.vocabularySetId now optional, added optional Game.exerciseSetId
- lib/gemini.ts: generateVocabularySet() calls Gemini with lesson content,
  scales item count to lesson length (6-30 items), validates response with zod
- POST /api/lessons/[id]/generate: creates an ExerciseSet for a lesson
  (VOCABULARY implemented; GRAMMAR/LISTENING_WRITING/SPEAKING return 501
  until their generator functions are added)
- Added GEMINI_API_KEY to .env.example

Note: migration.sql was hand-written (no DB access in this environment to
run 'prisma migrate dev'). Please review it and run it against a dev DB
before merging, then run 'npx prisma generate' locally.
